Class: ConnectorServer

ConnectorServer(businessNetworkCardStore, connectionProfileManager, socket)

A connector server for hosting Composer connectors and
serving them over a connected socket.io socket.

Constructor

new ConnectorServer(businessNetworkCardStore, connectionProfileManager, socket)

Constructor.

Parameters:
Name Type Description
businessNetworkCardStore BusinessNetworkCardStore

The business network card store to use.
connectionProfileManager ConnectionProfileManager

The connection profile manager to use.
socket Socket

The connected socket to use for communicating with the client.
